{
  "stem": "19441.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So somehow I said, and what's yours?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said Irma.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, nice to know you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And with that thing, I established myself as certain respect with her, that I as a prisoner ask her what's your name and told her nice to know you.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] When I think back, it-- it's silly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But for her, it was that probably the way they explained that the Jews are very weaklings or how you say the other?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm not sure what word you want.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like, you know, they are afraid to-- to speak up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- and here is somebody who not only spoke up, but she spoke up and she asked her name.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I asked the name of SS woman and tell her-- so anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that-- that what I did for a while, making the bed, the same thing, the cleaning up, helping.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and making sure that the people are out for the-- for roll call.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Tell me about roll call.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Birkenau, what would happen for roll call?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Roll call was a terrible thing, because people came so tired home and so uncomfortable was the sleeping and they was sick and weak.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they-- in the morning, they felt not to get up from bed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the appell had to stand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the counting had to be done, because still the counting wasn't done until the number didn't-- being perfect. 'Til then, the people had to stand.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had to say, come on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We must go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have to be counted, so-- and then they let us stand for hours.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Imagine first it was cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then it was warn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then it was tiring.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was-- it took us always hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
